The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Short break for Viru, Raina 
                                                                                                                       7                                      Short break for Viru, Raina 
            A STAFF REPORTER                      
	Calcutta: Two of Indias biggest performers, Virender Sehwag and Suresh Raina, who are currently touring Sri Lanka with Team India, returned home for a couple of days.         
	The duo came on Thursday and will be re-joining the squad on Saturday.         
	India lost their first match of the tri-series, against New Zealand, on Tuesday, by a mammoth margin of 200 runs. Their next match is against hosts Sri Lanka, in Dambulla, on Monday.                                                                                                                     
